OL,3,CPolice seize power tools believed to
OL,4,Chave been stolen
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof handling stolen goods in connection
OL,8,Fwith a selection of tools which have
OL,9,Fbeen seized by police.
OL,11,FOfficers in the New Forest have
OL,12,Freleased a series of images of the
OL,13,Ftools which are believed to have been
OL,14,Fstolen.
OL,16,FThey say they have come into
OL,17,Fpossession of items including an axe,
OL,18,Fpower tools, a racing bike and a saw.
