OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782146887
OL,3,CPolice seize power tools believed to
OL,4,Chave been stolen
OL,6,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are looking to identify their
OL,8,Frightful owners.
OL,10,F"Could they be yours?
OL,12,F"As part of enquiries, a 22-year-old
OL,13,Fman has been arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Fhandling stolen goods and has been
OL,15,Fbailed until 28 August while enquiries
OL,16,Fcontinue.
OL,18,F"If you believe any of these items to
OL,19,Fbe yours, please contact police on
OL,20,F101, quoting 44260246421."
